OL,3,CProtest against anti-Sikh hate crimes
OL,4,Cheld after killing of Kirandeep Kaur
OL,6,FMore than a hundred protesters
OL,7,Fgathered in Hayes to demonstrate
OL,8,Fagainst anti-Sikh hate crimes, and
OL,9,Fdemand justice for the killing of
OL,10,FKirandeep Kaur.
OL,12,FThey marched around Kaur's former
OL,13,Fneighbourhood in Hayes, expressing
OL,14,Fanger towards the rise of attacks on
OL,15,Fthe Sikh community.
OL,17,F24-year-old Kaur was killed after a
OL,18,Fman allegedly broke into her home and
OL,19,Fstabbed her to death as she slept in
OL,20,Fbed with her husband and three-month-
OL,21,Fold baby, a court heard on Thursday.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/4
