PN,37902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1784652479
OL,3,CProtest against anti-Sikh hate crimes
OL,4,Cheld after killing of Kirandeep Kaur
OL,6,FPolice have arrested and charged a 46-
OL,7,Fyear-old man, named Daniel Sean James,
OL,8,Fwith Kaur's murder.
OL,10,F"A woman being killed in her bed - I
OL,11,Fthink that's the most shocking thing
OL,12,FI've heard in a long time," said
OL,13,FNarinder Kaur, who attended the
OL,14,Fprotest.
OL,16,F"I think for the Sikh community,
OL,17,Fenough is enough.
OL,19,F"We're just really sad. This is a
OL,20,Ftragedy."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/4
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
