OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1784652479
OL,3,CProtest against anti-Sikh hate crimes
OL,4,Cheld after killing of Kirandeep Kaur
OL,6,FMany attendees at the protest blamed
OL,7,Ffar-right politicians and rhetoric for
OL,8,Fthe rise in anti-Sikh attacks.
OL,10,FThe Labour MP for Hayes and
OL,11,FHarlington, John McDonnell, attended
OL,12,Fthe protest.
OL,14,F"This is an absolute tragedy - it's
OL,15,Fshocked the whole community," he said.
OL,17,F"But the whole community has come
OL,18,Ftogether in solidarity.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/4
