PN,37904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1784652479
OL,3,CProtest against anti-Sikh hate crimes
OL,4,Cheld after killing of Kirandeep Kaur
OL,6,F"People of the Sikh community have
OL,7,Ffelt particularly at risk, but people
OL,8,Fof all denominations have arrived here
OL,9,Fin support."
OL,11,FHundreds of people are expected to
OL,12,Fgather in Hayes again on Sunday, to
OL,13,Fhold a candlelit vigil in Kirandeep's
OL,14,Fmemory.
OL,16,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,17,Four political experts are across all
OL,18,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,19,Fto the latest episode below...
